=I'm looking for jobs. Your task is to filter them based on a list of attributes and skills that I have. Some jobs may not be relevant, which is why I want you to go through each of them and then let me know whether or not I'm an OK fit.
Below is a Here is a my resume: {{ $json.content}}

Here is the job posting information:
Company Name: {{ $('Limit 5').item.json.companyName }}
Job Description: {{ $('Limit 5').item.json.descriptionHtml }}

Respond in this JSON format:
("verdict":"true or false"}
I
If I'm a fit, return true. If I'm not a fit, return false (both strings).

